xterm.js (including fit and web-links addons)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Terminal emulator front-end vendored in both web surfaces (xterm 5.5.0, fit
0.10.0, web-links 0.11.0), used by the managed terminals.

  Project:  https://github.com/xtermjs/xterm.js
  License:  MIT License
  Complete license: third_party/licenses/xterm.js-LICENSE

