Coding-agent CLIs and tools
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ShellTeam installs and orchestrates the following CLIs, each distributed under
its own license by its respective vendor (installed at setup time, not
redistributed in this repo):

  @anthropic-ai/claude-code   (Anthropic, via npm)
  @openai/codex               (OpenAI, via npm)
  agy — Antigravity CLI       (Google, verified release archive)
  opencode-ai                 (opencode, via npm)
  @upstash/context7-mcp       (Upstash, via npm)
  gh — GitHub CLI             (GitHub, via apt)

